    <title> CheckPoint: Torque </title>
    
      <p>A square plate ABCD with a side d is acted upon by several forces of equal magnitude F as shown. Point E is the center of the square, G is the midpoint of BC, K is the midpoint of CD, and L is the midpoint of AD.

</p>
